&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end lifecycle management across complex healthcare implementations, from solution design and contracting through execution and ongoing optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
