&lt;li&gt;Translating data into actionable insights that drive talent and business outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influencing and partnering with senior leaders to drive organizational effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading and developing high-performing teams while staying close to execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigating ambiguity and operating with ownership in fast-paced, evolving environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
