&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Establish and deepen executive relationships across C-suite, IT, security, and digital transformation leaders, positioning CLEAR as a trusted identity partner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
