&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLEAR is building THE secure identity company of the future. Our mission is to make experiences safer and easier—physically and digitally. With more than 38 million Members and a growing network of partners across the world, CLEAR&#39;s secure identity platform is transforming the way people live, work, and travel. Whether it’s at the airport, stadium, or throughout your everyday life, CLEAR unlocks the magic of frictionless experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Senior Director of Product Design to lead the vision, strategy, and execution for CLEAR Travel and CLEAR1 experiences across consumer and enterprise touchpoints including web, mobile, partner integrations, airport experiences, and in-person kiosks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly strategic leadership role for a design executive who can unify physical and digital experiences and build the operating model and design systems needed to scale. This leader will partner closely with Product, Engineering, Operations, and business leadership to ensure design drives measurable impact across growth, trust, throughput, and partner value.&lt;/p&gt;
