&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Product, Engineering, Aviation Operations, CLEAR1, Marketing, Partnerships, and Member Care to define priorities, shape roadmaps, and deliver high-impact experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the design of key traveler and partner journeys, including enrollment, verification, authentication, subscription, account management, and operational workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
